OL,3,CPM to urge 'whole of society' response
OL,4,Cto antisemitism in Downing Street talks
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will meet senior
OL,7,Ffigures from across public life in a
OL,8,Fbid to drive forward a "whole of
OL,9,Fsociety" response to antisemitism in
OL,10,Fthe wake of the Golders Green
OL,11,Fstabbings.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister will warn everyone
OL,14,Fhas a responsibility to stand with
OL,15,FJewish communities as attacks on
OL,16,FBritish Jews are "a crisis for all of
OL,17,Fus" and "a test of our values".
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@HO]xD@ROUyD@CO]yD@IOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
