PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777950276
OL,3,CPM to urge 'whole of society' response
OL,4,Cto antisemitism in Downing Street talks
OL,6,FSir Keir will convene meetings with
OL,7,Fleaders from business, civil society,
OL,8,Fhealth, culture, higher education and
OL,9,Fpolicing, during which he will ask
OL,10,Fattendees to reflect on how they can
OL,11,Fmove forward "at pace" to tackle
OL,12,Fantisemitism in their sector.
OL,14,FHe will also focus on the domestic
OL,15,Fsecurity implications of the Iran war,
OL,16,Fincluding a heightened threat to
OL,17,FJewish communities, during a
OL,18,Fministerial meeting of the Middle East
OL,19,FResponse Committee, the crisis team
OL,20,Fset up to respond to conflict.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
