OL,3,CPM to urge 'whole of society' response
OL,4,Cto antisemitism in Downing Street talks
OL,6,FOpening a series of roundtable
OL,7,Fdiscussions on Tuesday, Sir Keir is
OL,8,Fexpected to say: "Last week's
OL,9,Fterrorist attack in Golders Green was
OL,10,Futterly appalling.
OL,12,F"But it was not an isolated incident.
OL,14,F"It is part of a pattern of rising
OL,15,Fantisemitism that has left our Jewish
OL,16,Fcommunities feeling frightened, angry,
OL,17,Fand asking whether this country, their
OL,18,Fhome, is safe for them.
OL,26,@pD@ROUtD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777950276
OL,3,CPM to urge 'whole of society' response
OL,4,Cto antisemitism in Downing Street talks
OL,6,F"These disgusting attacks are being
OL,7,Fmade against British Jews. But, make
OL,8,Fno mistake, this crisis ` it is a
OL,9,Fcrisis for all of us. It is a test of
OL,10,Four values.
OL,12,F"Values that are not guaranteed, but
OL,13,Fare earned. Every single day, through
OL,14,Four actions.
OL,16,F"So, it is not enough to simply say we
OL,17,Fstand with Jewish communities. We must
OL,18,Fshow it. And that responsibility lies
OL,19,Fwith each and every one of us.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777950276
OL,3,CPM to urge 'whole of society' response
OL,4,Cto antisemitism in Downing Street talks
OL,6,F"That is what today is about. Because
OL,7,Fonly by working together can we
OL,8,Feradicate antisemitism from every
OL,9,Fcorner of society."
OL,11,FIt comes after two Jewish men, Shloime
OL,12,FRand, 34, and Norman Shine, 76, were
OL,13,Fstabbed during a knife rampage through
OL,14,Fthe streets of the Golders Green north
OL,15,FLondon suburb last week.
OL,17,FAlleged attacker Essa Suleiman, 45,
OL,18,Fappeared at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,19,FCourt on Friday and was remanded in
OL,20,Fcustody.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
