OL,3,CPM to urge 'whole of society' response
OL,4,Cto antisemitism in Downing Street talks
OL,6,FThe attack, which has been declared a
OL,7,Fterror incident by police, is the
OL,8,Flatest in a string of violent
OL,9,Fincidents against Jewish people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
